node.text:
You know Barbie, but have you met… Barbie? 💖 That’s right; Barbie Roberts meets Barbie Roberts, and they have more in common than just their name! The two became fast friends and chose nicknames inspired by their hometowns – Malibu and Brooklyn – to better differentiate when they’re together.
 
Gather your kids and join the two friends in this dorm room unboxing to get to know #Barbie “Brooklyn” Roberts!

node.text: Saturday calls for grocery shopping! From candy favorites to fresh veggies, the Chelsea Snack Stand has everything you need. Grab a snack and shop with Barbie and Chelsea now! 🍎🍞🍭

node.text: Paging Dr. Barbie! 🩺 In 1973, #Barbie broke the glass ceiling to earn her diploma and become a doctor for the first time. Now collectors can shop the landmark career doll, complete with crisp lab coat and surgical scrubs, perfect for providing care in and out of the operating room.

node.text: Together we have the power to make the world a better place by living up to our full potential. Barbie is committed to shaping a future where every girl knows that her voice matters. This #WomensEqualityDay, remind a girl in your life to continue to dream big. #YouCanBeAnything
